                <supplied reason="lost">Toto orbe</supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">pacifi</supplied>co con<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>omino</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostro</ex></expan></supplied> Honorio Pio <lb n="4"/>Felici victori <lb n="5"/>ac triumfatori <lb n="6"/>semper Augusto <lb n="7"/>Lepcitani devoti <lb n="8"/>numini maiesta<lb break="no" n="9"/>tique eius
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The inscription is carved over an erased earlier text (of which some letters remain); two other erased inscriptions are on two other sides.</p>
